**<<< RULES >>>**
As any civilized Society that lasts longer than 1 day, we have rules. Rules must be followed so that we are fair to one another and so that chaos won't wreck everything that's been worked for. So without further ado, here are the rules of this server.

**1.** Please do not swear every 15 seconds, we're fine with swearing but don't just say shit every 15 seconds or spam fuck because you feel like it. We have the right to mute you any time from the respective channel if you do.
**2.** Remember to follow discord's Terms of Service.
**3.** No Racism, Misogyny or Misandry and do NOT play victim or shove your beliefs in others. We are trying to have a toxic free environment. The popular opinion is never always correct.
**4.** NSFW content is not allowed
**5.** Raiders, we will instant ban and report
**6.** If all is good, welcome and it is a rule to enjoy your life! Hope you have a nice time here!
